{
  "page": "Sweets",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For other uses, see <a href=\"/index.php/Sweet_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Sweet (disambiguation)\">Sweet (disambiguation)</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Sweets</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Sweets.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Sweets.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/98/Sweets.jpg/350px-Sweets.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"352\" srcset=\"/images/9/98/Sweets.jpg 1.5x\" /></a><div>Sweets, by Pojypojy ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_of_Qaggaz\" title=\"House of Qaggaz\">House of Qaggaz</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian\" title=\"Valyrian\">Valyrian</a> <small>(possibly)</small><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafsweets.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafsweets.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafsweets.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafsweets.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Lover</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Yezzan_zo_Qaggaz\" title=\"Yezzan zo Qaggaz\">Yezzan zo Qaggaz</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Sweets</b> is a hermaphrodite<sup id=\"cite_ref-hermaphrodite_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-hermaphrodite-5\">&#91;N 2&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Slave\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Slave\">slave</a> owned by <a href=\"/index.php/Yezzan_zo_Qaggaz\" title=\"Yezzan zo Qaggaz\">Yezzan zo Qaggaz</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sweets&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Sweets\" title=\"Category:Images of Sweets\">Images of Sweets</a></div>\n<p>Sweets has a willowy body, and has <a href=\"/index.php/Hair_dye\" title=\"Hair dye\">dyed</a> purple hair and <a href=\"/index.php/Violet_eyes\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Violet eyes\">violet eyes</a>. Sweets dresses in <a href=\"/index.php/Moonstone\" title=\"Moonstone\">moonstones</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\">Myrish</a> lace. Sweets is fluent in four tongues, one of them <a href=\"/index.php/High_Valyrian\" title=\"High Valyrian\">High Valyrian</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Sweets is rather droll and astute - she titters a ghastly titter at <a href=\"/index.php/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a>'s naïveté as to their fate if Yezzan dies. Sweets is fond of her master, Yezzan. Because Sweets is Yezzan's \"special pet\", indulged and favored, she is hated by Yezzan's other slaves.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Sweets is referred to alternately by the pronouns she/her by <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> but occasionally as he/him, by Tyrion and by Yezzan's serjeant <a href=\"/index.php/Scar\" title=\"Scar\">Scar</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> When first meeting Tyrion and Penny, Sweets guesses that they are trying to decide whether she is a man or a woman and tells them she is both, revealing what is under her skirts.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sweets&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sweets&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Sweets_by_Sanrixian.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9b/Sweets_by_Sanrixian.jpg/350px-Sweets_by_Sanrixian.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9b/Sweets_by_Sanrixian.jpg/525px-Sweets_by_Sanrixian.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9b/Sweets_by_Sanrixian.jpg/700px-Sweets_by_Sanrixian.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Sweets_by_Sanrixian.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Sweets, by Sanrixian ©</div></div></div>\n<p>Along with the rest of <a href=\"/index.php/Yezzan_zo_Qaggaz\" title=\"Yezzan zo Qaggaz\">Yezzan zo Qaggaz</a>'s \"special treasures\", Sweets accompanies her master to the <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\">Yunkai</a> encampment outside of <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>. During the <a href=\"/index.php/Windblown\" title=\"Windblown\">Windblown</a>'s march to <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Dick_Straw\" title=\"Dick Straw\">Dick Straw</a> tells <a href=\"/index.php/Quentyn_Martell\" title=\"Quentyn Martell\">Quentyn Martell</a> some of the gossip about Yezzan and his passion for grotesques, including word that among his slaves is a hermaphrodite<sup id=\"cite_ref-hermaphrodite_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-hermaphrodite-5\">&#91;N 2&#93;</a></sup> who warms his bed at night.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Yezzan purchases <a href=\"/index.php/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> for his <a href=\"/index.php/Grotesquerie\" title=\"Grotesquerie\">grotesquerie</a>. His overseer, <a href=\"/index.php/Nurse\" title=\"Nurse\">Nurse</a>, introduces them to Sweets, who reveals what is under her skirts. Sweets is loathed by some slaves because she is the master's favorite, but she is friendly and candid with Tyrion and Penny, warning them to be careful around Nurse.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Sweets identifies <a href=\"/index.php/Ben_Plumm\" title=\"Ben Plumm\">Ben Plumm</a> to Tyrion, before he and Penny are summoned to perform during Yezzan's banquet held in <a href=\"/index.php/Yurkhaz_zo_Yunzak\" title=\"Yurkhaz zo Yunzak\">Yurkhaz zo Yunzak</a>'s honor.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When Yezzan contracts the <a href=\"/index.php/Pale_mare\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Pale mare\">pale mare</a>, it falls to Sweets, Penny, Tyrion, and his other treasures to attend to him. Tyrion thinks to himself that Sweets was right in that Yezzan was not so bad as masters went. When Tyrion tells Penny sardonically that they are all going to die, Sweets gives them a desperate look, and replies that Yezzan \"must not die\". Unlike Penny, Sweets is under no illusions as to their fate if Yezzan dies. She remarks to Penny that favorites sometimes accompany their masters to the grave and serve him in the afterlife. Tyrion thinks that Sweets should know, as his will be the first throat slit.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When the <a href=\"/index.php/Goat_boy\" title=\"Goat boy\">goat boy</a> hopefully mentions the slave-freeing Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>, Sweets replies that she is dead, drowned in the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_Sea\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dothraki Sea\">Dothraki Sea</a>, either not knowing that the Dothraki Sea is grassland and not water, or making an ironic pun. When Tyrion informs Sweets that they will see to fetching fresh water for the master, Sweets sounds numb when she replies that this is good of Tyrion, causing Tyrion to realize that Sweets's numbness is caused by more than just the fear of being killed - Sweets had truly been fond of Yezzan, the only one of Yezzan's treasures to feel that way.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Tyrion uses the task of fetching water to escape with Penny, as well as his knowledge of how Yezzan's other slaves feel about Sweets. Tyrion commands Yezzan's brutal and stupid serjeant, <a href=\"/index.php/Scar\" title=\"Scar\">Scar</a>, to take pails and fetch water, and when Scar is insulted at being ordered around by a slave and strikes him, Tyrion claims that Sweets said Yezzan must have water. Scar insults Sweets, saying he doesn't take orders from him either. Scar orders Tyrion and Penny to fetch the water, and Tyrion manipulates him into letting them go with <a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a> as well. As they are escaping to the camp of the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Sons\" title=\"Second Sons\">Second Sons</a>, Penny becomes distressed at leaving her animals, <a href=\"/index.php/Pretty_Pig\" title=\"Pretty Pig\">Pretty Pig</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Dog\" title=\"Dog\">dog</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Crunch\" title=\"Crunch\">Crunch</a>, and Tyrion lies to her and says Sweets will make sure they're taken care of.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Later in the Second Sons' camp, Penny says they had been better off with Yezzan, saying they were his favorites, like Sweets. To shock Penny out of her listlessness, Tyrion lies to her and tells her that Yezzan's special slaves are all dead from the pale mare, and that Sweets was the first to go.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> The fate of Sweets is unknown, although according to a semi-canon source, she did die of the pale mare.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafsweets.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafsweets.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sweets&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>You are trying to decide if I'm a man or woman. I'm both, and <a href=\"/index.php/Yezzan_zo_Qaggaz\" title=\"Yezzan zo Qaggaz\">master</a> loves me best.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Sweets, to <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Sweets:</b> <a href=\"/index.php/Yezzan_zo_Qaggaz\" title=\"Yezzan zo Qaggaz\">Yezzan</a> must not die.<br /> \n</p><p><b>Penny:</b> Some masters free their <a href=\"/index.php/Slaves\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Slaves\">slaves</a> when they die.<br /> \n</p>\n<b>Sweets:</b> Only favorites. They free them from the woes of the world, to accompany their beloved master to the grave and serve him in the afterlife.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Sweets and <a href=\"/index.php/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>His will be the first throat slit.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a>'s thoughts on Sweets's fate if Yezzan dies</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Sweets sounded numb. It was more than just fear of having her throat cut; alone amongst <a href=\"/index.php/Yezzan_zo_Qaggaz\" title=\"Yezzan zo Qaggaz\">Yezzan</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Grotesquerie\" title=\"Grotesquerie\">treasures</a>, she actually seemed fond of their immense master.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Tyrion:</b> Sweets said <a href=\"/index.php/Yezzan_zo_Qaggaz\" title=\"Yezzan zo Qaggaz\">the master</a> must have water.<br />\n<b>Scar:</b> Sweets can go fuck himself. He's made for it. We don't take commands from that freak neither.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Scar\" title=\"Scar\">Scar</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The hermaphrodite had long been their master's special pet, indulged and favored, and the noble <a href=\"/index.php/Yezzan_zo_Qaggaz\" title=\"Yezzan zo Qaggaz\">Yezzan</a>'s other <a href=\"/index.php/Slave\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Slave\">slaves</a> hated him for it.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sweets&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">An assumption based on Sweets's <a href=\"/index.php/Purple_eyes\" title=\"Purple eyes\">purple eyes</a>.  <a href=\"/index.php/High_Valyrian\" title=\"High Valyrian\">High Valyrian</a> is also one of the four languages that Sweets speaks fluently. However, as people not of <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian\" title=\"Valyrian\">Valyrian</a> descent, like the members of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne\" title=\"House Dayne\">House Dayne</a>, may also have purple eyes,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rssm1428.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rssm1428.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> and some non-Valyrians speak High Valyrian, it may not be correct.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-hermaphrodite-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-hermaphrodite_5-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-hermaphrodite_5-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Equivalent to <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Intersex\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Intersex\">intersex</a> in the real-world. \"Hermaphrodite\" is the term used in the novel, and conveys by association the beliefs and attitudes regarding intersex conditions that one would find in the setting.<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sweets&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rssm1428.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rssm1428.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/So_Spake_Martin\" title=\"So Spake Martin\">So Spake Martin</a>: <i><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.westeros.org/Citadel/SSM/Entry/1428\">Event Horizon Chat</a></i> (March 18, 1999).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafsweets.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafsweets.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafsweets.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafsweets.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\">2.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Sweets.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/Special:Diff/196611\" title=\"Special:Diff/196611\">wiki comment</a> by <a href=\"/index.php/User:Ran\" title=\"User:Ran\">Elio Garcia</a> (January 9, 2017)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\">4.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-2\">4.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-3\">4.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-4\">4.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-5\">4.5</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-6\">4.6</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_47\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 47\">Chapter 47</a>, Tyrion X.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\">5.00</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-1\">5.01</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-2\">5.02</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-3\">5.03</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-4\">5.04</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-5\">5.05</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-6\">5.06</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-7\">5.07</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-8\">5.08</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-9\">5.09</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-10\">5.10</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_57\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 57\">Chapter 57</a>, Tyrion XI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_25\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 25\">Chapter 25</a>, The Windblown.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_66\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 66\">Chapter 66</a>, Tyrion XII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404015608\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.126 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.333 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 2825/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 11945/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 16241/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 3482/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 14/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 1/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 9487/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.180/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 7.77 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  311.980      1 -total\n 77.03%  240.306      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 76.65%  239.132      1 Template:Infobox\n 14.16%   44.178     24 Template:Ref\n 10.41%   32.467     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  9.81%   30.610     24 Template:Ref/core\n  9.62%   29.999      1 Template:For\n  4.86%   15.173      3 Template:Refn\n  4.31%   13.440      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  3.00%    9.373      6 Template:Quote\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:8277-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404015608 and revision id 333949\n -->\n",
